text: Novoprokhladnoe () is a rural locality (a selo) in Dakhovskoye Rural Settlement of Maykopsky District, Russia. The population was 119 as of 2018. There are 5 streets. == Geography == The village is located in the valley of the Sakhray River, 16 km from Dakhovskaya. == References == Category:Rural localities in Maykopsky District
title: Novoprokhladnoe
